  'City of Cape Town Bursary South Africa 2026',
  'CITY OF CAPE TOWN',
  'Applicants must satisfy the following minimum entry criteria before applying (please note that failure to satisfy all the requirements will lead to your application not being considered): You must be a South African citizen You must reside in Cape Town, in the Western Cape pro...',
