(
  'Hessequa Local Municipality Bursary South Africa 2025',
  'HESSEQUA MUNICIPALITY',
  'Students will be paid a stipend, which must be used for meals, accommodation and transport costs. The bursary will be awarded for 1 year of study. Theoretical training will take place at the institution and the practical work experience will take place in Riversdale. www.zabur...',
  NULL,
