  'KwaDukuza Municipality Bursary South Africa 2026',
  'KWADUKUZA MUNICIPALITY',
  'The bursary will cover the following expenses: registration or admission fees to the value of R10 000. www.zabursaries.co.za is committed to keeping you up to date with the latest bursary opportunities, and this article covers all details about the KwaDukuza Municipality Bursa...',
