  'Applications must be submitted online at: Mpumalanga Provincial Government Bursary Application 2026 Enter “www.zabursaries.co.za” in the field asking how you heard about the Mpumalanga Provincial Government Bursary. Submit clear copies of the following supporting documentation along with your online application (the submission of these documents is compulsory – if any items are missing, your application may be disqualified): ID Document (certified copy) Curriculum Vitae Education and qualification achievements (certified copies) Proof of registration at a recognised institution Proof of residence Parents or guardians proof of income (latest payslips if employed/ affidavit if unemployed/ proof of sassa grant or pension if applicable/ certified death certificate if deceased) Applications must be submitted in one of the following ways: - Email: otprecruitment@mpg.gov.za (Insert the words " Mpumalanga Provincial Government Bursary 2026 " in the email subject line). - Hand delivery: Office of the Premier Makhonjwa Building 1st floor Government Boulevard Riverside Park - Post: The Assistant Director: Internal HRU &#038; Ms MK Ngomane Private Bag X11291 Mbombela 1200',
