(
  'W&RSETA Bursary South Africa 2021 - 2022',
  'W&RSETA Bursary South Africa 2021 - 2022',
  'W&RSETA will be awarding 2000 bursaries to new unemployed TVET students and 1000 bursaries to new unemployed HET students. The bursary programme is open to students who are studying (or intend to study) within the Wholesale and Retail Sector Scarce Skills, particularly the fol...',
