  'Applications must be submitted online at: Hollywood Foundation "Future is Bright" Bursary Application 2026 Enter “www.zabursaries.co.za” in the field asking how you heard about the Hollywood Foundation bursary. Submit clear copies of the following supporting documentation along with your online application (the submission of these documents is compulsory – if any items are missing, your application may be disqualified): ID document (certified copy) Matric certificate/statement of results Most recent academic results (final or interim, as applicable) Acceptance letter/ proof of application from your institution (on institutions letterhead) Detailed information regarding the chosen qualification Name and address of the registered institution Proforma invoice/ estimate invoice from your institution (must be broken down into: registration fees, tuition fees, prescribed study materials or textbooks, accommodation and living assistance (if applicable)) Proof of banking details of the registered institution Proof of address (affidavit or utility bill) Motivational letter, written in your own words - explaining why you are applying and how the bursary will support your studies (maximum 2000 words) (read our tips on how to write a motivational letter for your bursary application )',
  'Commerce',
