  'Applications must be submitted online at: Investec Tech Scholarship Application 2026 Enter “www.zabursaries.co.za” in the field asking how you heard about the Investec Tech Scholarship. Applicants must read the StudyTrust bursary instructions page before applying. Submit clear copies of the following supporting documentation along with your online application (the submission of these documents is compulsory - if any items are missing, your application may be disqualified): South African ID document (certified copy) Matric certificate (certified copy) Full academic record/ transcripts (certified copy)',
