  ARRAY['https://advtech.ci.hr/applicant/index.php']::text[],
  'The bursary will provide cover for tuition fees (the amount of cover will be linked to students academic performance). Bursary recipients will also receive the following benefits: The opportunity to study full-time or part-time at a recognised institution The opportunity to partake in a mentorship programme The opportunity to complete at least 1 essential practical work component at a school within the ADvTECH Schools Division (where feasible) The opportunity to partake in paid school activities (such as sports coaching, music coaching or teaching assistant) The opportunity to be placed in one of the Schools within the ADvTECH Schools Division after graduation (after completing the bursary and if a position is available)',
