  'Applications must be submitted online at: ADvTECH Student Teacher Bursary Application 2022 Submit clear copies of the following documentation along with your online application (the submission of these documents is compulsory – if any items are missing, your application may be disqualified): ID document (certified copy) Matric certificate (certified copy) Full academic record (on institutions letterhead) Curriculum Vitae',
