  'EMFULENI LOCAL MUNICIPALITY',
  'Applicants must satisfy the following minimum entry criteria before applying for the bursary (please note that failure to satisfy all the requirements will lead to your application not being considered): You must be a South African citizen You must reside within Emfuleni Local...',
